chav1961.purelib.basic

Interface GettersAndSettersFactory.GetterAndSetter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GettersAndSettersFactory.BooleanGetterAndSetter, GettersAndSettersFactory.ByteGetterAndSetter, GettersAndSettersFactory.CharGetterAndSetter, GettersAndSettersFactory.DoubleGetterAndSetter, GettersAndSettersFactory.FloatGetterAndSetter, GettersAndSettersFactory.IntGetterAndSetter, GettersAndSettersFactory.LongGetterAndSetter, GettersAndSettersFactory.ObjectGetterAndSetter, GettersAndSettersFactory.ShortGetterAndSetter
    Enclosing class:
    GettersAndSettersFactory

    public static interface GettersAndSettersFactory.GetterAndSetter

    This interface can be used as type of variable to store any getter and setter instance. All getters and setters implement this interface, so all of them can be casted to it

    Since:
    0.0.2
    Author:
    Alexander Chernomyrdin aka chav1961
